reviewText: Love Bollywood films. This one had a good story and a bittersweet ending. Saif Ali Khan and Katrina Kaif work well together in this BW drama.

this is a great movie, the story gets your attention right from the beginning.  with all the terror attacks going happening around the globe wish that these stories could be just like this.  this movie received bad reviews but i totally enjoyed it, don't believe other companies reviews if you like suspense and action watch this movie
